data.description: Welcome to your new home, this beautiful double-wide manufactured home sitting on its own lot has everything you need and more. With high end features such as granite and built in appliances, you will feel like a professional chef in your own kitchen. The engineered wood floors add a touch of elegance. The cute front porch is a perfect place to relax and enjoy the beautiful landscaping. Comes complete with a tool shed perfect for storing your gardening tools and more. This home has been well maintained and looking for it's new owner!
